# =============================================================================
# Enterprise Mediator Platform (EMP) — root .gitignore
# Polyrepo: .NET 8 services, Next.js frontend, Terraform, Docker
# =============================================================================

# --- Operating system ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

